## Target venue

QSS (Quantitative Science Studies) — open access, MIT Press, computational
scientometrics audience, higher IF (~6.5).

## Exit criteria

Companion paper submitted to QSS. Multi-layer framework validated on
climate finance corpus. Transition zones reported with Z-scores and
censored-gap confirmation. Honest about growth-bias correction.
